nodes.text: Kelin Dass was a Jedi Knight who at one point in history served the Jedi Order. An obscure philosopher within the Order's long history, he authored a series of untitled musings and poetry. At least one copy was stored within the archives of the Jedi Sanctuary on Delriss, where it survived the Clone Wars in the abandon facility.
